You'll need these four systems to complete this tutorial:

* Your workstation
* A node to manage
* A dedicated server to run Chef server
* A dedicated server to run Chef Analytics

Chef server and Chef Analytics must exist on separate systems due to the heavy processing requirements of Chef Analytics.
